snippet.title: Rocket Santa 2
snippet.description: Rocket Santa 2 Launch game. Launch Santa up in the air with a big canon and sttrap on rockets to reach the moon.

snippet.title: Gibbets: Santa In Trouble
snippet.description: Gibbets: Santa In Trouble Skill game. Use bow and arrow to cut the ropes and release the santa's that are hanging.

snippet.title: 60 Seconds Santa Run
snippet.description: 60 Seconds Santa Run Action game. Let Santa run as fast as possible to reach the busstop for a sleigh.

snippet.title: Santa Rockstar 5: Rudolf Saves The World
snippet.description: Santa Rockstar 5: Rudolf Saves The World Skill game. Help out Santa and control the guitar skills of Rudolf to save xmas!

snippet.title: Slay With Santa
snippet.description: Slay With Santa Action game. Help Santa to retrieve the presents from the ugly creatures that try to damage xmas.

snippet.title: Santa's Castle Defense
snippet.description: Santa's Castle Defense Shooting game. Try to defend the castle of Santa against the army of the Grinch.

snippet.title: Sling Shot Santa
snippet.description: Sling Shot Santa Throw Santa as far as you can over the ravine. Try to throw him over 300 meters away for a surprise.

snippet.title: Santas Chimney Trouble
snippet.description: Santas Chimney Trouble Repair the connection between the fireplace and the chimney before Santa arrives.

snippet.title: Swords and Sandals 2: Emperor's Reign
snippet.description: Swords and Sandals 2: Emperor's Reign New ranged weapons, magic spells and powerful new champions to battle.

snippet.title: Swords and Sandals 3: Solo Ultratus
snippet.description: Swords and Sandals 3: Solo Ultratus RPG style gladiator fighting game. Fight the realm's most powerful champions.
